#HEADER_START
/*
 * High Tides for TTL 5.
 * Edited by T-West, December 2025.
 * Based on the map by AlgernonR, later modified by Chrazini.
 *
 * Hidden Cup 5 Adjustments
 * - Reduce the number of rocks in the southern corner.
 * - Reduce the number of Crocodiles in the southern corner.
 * - Reduce the number of straggler trees in the southern corner.
 * - Reduce the number of Deep Fish.
 * - Add Shore Fish in the northern shallows.
 * - Add Shore Fish in the south.
 * - Increase Stone and Gold in the south.
 * - Add Hunt at the bottom.
 * - Remove Reeds from beaches.
 */

/*

	High Tide by AlgernonR
	Modified by Chrazini

	Created: 20-02-2021
	Version: 1.0
	BSV: 8.1.1
	Compatibility: Definitive Edition

	Theme: African
	Style: Land & Water
	Formation: Circle

	Please report bugs or requests on either:
	Steam: https://steamcommunity.com/id/chrazini
	Discord: Chrazini#5687
	AoEZone: https://www.aoezone.net/members/chrazini.48855/
	Voobly: https://www.voobly.com/profile/view/123721778

	Changelog 20-02-2021 | Version 1.0
	� Initial release.

*/
#HEADER_END

/*
 * Defeat players if the game mode is not set to random map.
 * Includes a check for the secondary game mode checkboxes.
 */
